# Title: RemCom Service Installation
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-08-07
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects RemCom service installation and execution events
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1569.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/system/service_control_manager/win_system_service_install_remcom.yml

EventID=7045 Provider_Name="Service Control Manager" ServiceName="RemComSvc" OR ImagePath="*\\RemComSvc.exe"